moduleDescription: This module aims to give students the opportunities to consolidate their practice in their area of Specialties under the guidance of a clinical preceptor. Students are given the option to be attached to the unit/ward where they will be serving their internship upon completion of the MN programme or another practised area offering similar learning experiences.
faculty: YONG LOO LIN SCHOOL OF MEDICINE
